{"title":"绝妙的供状","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝妙的供状"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　江有生画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬的供状，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面大有学问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列举事实许多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙在都不肯定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是“似乎”，又是“大约”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是“估计”，又是“确信”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么“据信”呀，“暗示”呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么“身份不明”呀，如此等等。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“确信”攻击的舰艇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向美舰发射了鱼雷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼雷发射了多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“无法”弄清！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“据信”这次攻击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延续了“大约”三小时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是“大约”呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也就是说不那么肯定！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“估计”对鱼雷艇的反击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是由驱逐舰的炮火进行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有两艘被击伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“至少”有两艘被打沉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然“至少”是两艘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可能比这还多也不一定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可能是百，可能是千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还可能更多，多得要命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“身份不明”的船只，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向美舰“迅速逼近”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是“身份不明”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是说不知是谁的舰艇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可能是朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可能是敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也可能什么也不是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑袋瓜子有毛病！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事实虽然不肯定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不妨作出结论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管他三七二十一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是假偏说真！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚无缥缈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半吐半吞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一纸供状，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下奇文！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有“学问！”有“学问！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方世界第一等！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗衣钵世代相传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从麦金莱到约翰逊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为总统对本团体的贡献而干杯！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}